name: Legally Operating Businesses
attribution: Department of Consumer and Worker Protection (DCWP)
description: NOTE: This dataset reflects data as of 7/21/2023. The Department of Consumer and Worker Protection (DCWP) is working on an updated version of this dataset. This dataset features licenses issued by DCWP to businesses and individuals so that they may legally operate in New York City. Note: Temporary street fair vendor permits are not included in this dataset.
